text: Sue Casey (April 8, 1926 â€“ February 21, 2019) was an American actress. She appeared in over 85 productions between the years 1945 and 2002. She was born in Los Angeles, California Casey starred in The Secret Life of Walter Mitty (1947), Neptune's Daughter (1949), Annie Get Your Gun (1950), Show Boat (1951), Rear Window (1954), Breakfast at Tiffany's (1961), Camelot (1967) and Paint Your Wagon (1969).
